DROP TABLE IF EXISTS Menu_clean;
CREATE TABLE Menu_clean (
"id" INT NULL,

"location" VARCHAR(255) NULL,
"location_cluster" VARCHAR(255) NULL,

"currency" VARCHAR(255) NULL,
"currency_symbol" VARCHAR(255) NULL,
"status" VARCHAR(255) NULL,
"page_count" VARCHAR(255) NULL,
"dish_count" VARCHAR(255) NULL
);
